name: LoveTime
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: love time
des: Have you ever wondered how long you've been in your relationship in terms of seconds, minutes, hours, days, weeks, months, or years? If so, with Love Time, you can quickly calculate your "Love Time" in all sorts of time formats. Amaze your significant other by telling them, in seconds, minutes, etc, how long you've been in your relationship!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
